{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Sering Digunakan Sebagai Caption, Tere Liye Larang Netizen Gunakan Quotes-nya","content":"<p>Penggunaan <em>caption </em>sebagai pelengkap konten kita di media sosial kayaknya sekarang udah menjadi hal yang penting. Rasanya gak lengkap kalau postingan kita gak ada <em>caption-</em>nya. Ide pembuatan <em>caption </em>ini bisa dari mana saja. Curahan hati, tulisan dari buku sampai mengutip kalimat seseorang.</p>\n<p>Belakangan ini, <em>caption </em>yang digunakan masyarakat Indonesia pada akun pribadi media sosial mereka diambil dari <em>quotes </em>dari <em>Fanpage</em> Facebook salah satu penulis ternama Indonesia, Tere Liye. Namanya juga penulis, jadi gak aneh kalau tulisannya sanggup menginspirasi para pembaca. Ibaratnya nih, tulisan Tere Liye sesederhana apapun itu udah bisa mewakili perasaan masyarakat.</p>\n<p>Sayangnya, beberapa hari yang lalu media sosial sempat dihebohkan oleh salah satu postingan Tere Liye di <em>Fanpage</em> Facebook-nya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41509\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41509\" data-attachment-id=\"41509\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/attachment/tere1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere1.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41509 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41509\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter</p></div></p>\n<p>Ternyata hal ini disebabkan oleh keresahannya terhadap masyarakat yang selalu menggunakan <em>quotes</em>-nya untuk pelengkap postingan di media sosial. Menurutnya banyak sekali postingan yang tidak nyambung dengan maksud dari <em>quotes</em> yang sudah dikutip.</p>\n<p>Banyak orang yang mengunggah foto <em>selfie</em>, momen makan bersama teman dan sebagainya lalu mencomot <em>quote</em> dari Tere Liye seperti “Inilah hidupku, dst dst – Tere Liye” sebagai <em>caption. </em>Tere Liye menganggap orang-orang yang melakukan hal itu seperti pamer namun bersembunyi dibalik kalimat sederhana. Seakan-akan mereka tidak melakukan apa-apa.</p>\n<p>Namanya juga media sosial, netizen yang mulia, langsung ramai memberi komentar. Dari mulai pro dan kontra, semua ada. Kebanyakan menilai kalau apa yang sudah ditulis di media (dalam hal ini Facebook) harusnya sudah menjadi milik bersama. Penulis sudah bukan pemegang kekuasaan lagi.</p>\n<p>Sesuatu yang ditaruh di media sosial sudah lumrah jadi bahan konsumsi masyarakat. Kalau gak mau dipakai orang lain ya jangan di taruh. Bahkan ada yang sampai mempermasalahkan gambar dari <em>cover Fanpage</em> Facebook Tere Liye .</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_29351\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-29351\" data-attachment-id=\"29351\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/attachment/isi-menulis-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-MENULIS-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tulisannya sih “Menulis Adalah Berbagi” tapi kok giliran sudah digunakan malah marah? Gimana ya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tulisannya sih “Menulis Adalah Berbagi” tapi kok giliran sudah digunakan malah marah? Gimana ya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-MENULIS-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-MENULIS-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-29351\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-MENULIS-1.jpg\" alt=\"Tulisannya sih “Menulis Adalah Berbagi” tapi kok giliran sudah digunakan malah marah? Gimana ya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-29351\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tulisannya sih “Menulis Adalah Berbagi” tapi kok giliran sudah digunakan malah marah? Gimana ya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)</p></div></p>\n<p>Banyak yang bilang kalau <em>cover Fanpage</em> Facebook dari Tere Liye tidak mencerminkan apa yang dia tulis selama ini. Memang Tere Liye di media sosial lebih dikenal dengan kata-katanya yang bijak namun juga menusuk di satu waktu. Gak heran kalau komentar-komentar “nyinyir” berdatangan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41510\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41510\" data-attachment-id=\"41510\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/attachment/tere2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41510 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere2.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41510\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41511\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41511\" data-attachment-id=\"41511\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/attachment/tere3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gimana tanggapannya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gimana tanggapannya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere3.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41511 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere3.jpg\" alt=\"Gimana tanggapannya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41511\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gimana tanggapannya? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41513\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41513\" data-attachment-id=\"41513\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/attachment/tere4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mba ini sepertinya emosi sekali. (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mba ini sepertinya emosi sekali. (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere4.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41513 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere4.jpg\" alt=\"Mba ini sepertinya emosi sekali. (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41513\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mba ini sepertinya emosi sekali. (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)</p></div></p>\n<p>Gak cuma mempermasalahkan cover Fanpage Facebook aja, tapi bahkan sampai pemakaian nama pena Tere Liye pun jadi ikut disinggung karena kejadian ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41514\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41514\" data-attachment-id=\"41514\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/attachment/tere5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hem, kira-kira gimana nih, Mas Tere Liye? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hem, kira-kira gimana nih, Mas Tere Liye? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere5.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41514 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere5.jpg\" alt=\"Hem, kira-kira gimana nih, Mas Tere Liye? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41514\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hem, kira-kira gimana nih, Mas Tere Liye? (Sumber: Fanpage Facebook @tereliyewriter)</p></div></p>\n<p>Oh iya, bro sis yang belum tau, Tere Liye itu adalah nama pena dari Om Darwis. Walaupun terdengar seperti nama seorang wanita, Tere Liye sebenarnya adalah sosok laki-laki sederhana. Dibalik kata-katanya yang terkadang menusuk, Tere Liye sampai saat ini sudah mempunyai 28 judul buku. Keren banget ya, bro sis! Gak heran kalau beliau sangat “menjaga” tulisannya. Tere Liye bahkan masih sempat untuk menyindir orang-orang yang merasa tesinggung dengan tulisannya di Facebook lewat salah satu bukunya yang berjudul “Negeri Para Bedebah”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41515\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41515\" data-attachment-id=\"41515\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/sering-digunakan-sebagai-caption-tere-liye-larang-netizen-gunakan-quotes-nya/attachment/tere6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.facebook.com/tereliyewriter/\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.facebook.com/tereliyewriter/&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere6.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-41515 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/tere6.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.facebook.com/tereliyewriter/\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/c